WEBVTT

00:01.350 --> 00:04.119
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.153 --> 00:06.621
(watch beeping)

00:06.655 --> 00:10.091
Oh! Good thing I set my watch,
otherwise I would've forgot

00:10.092 --> 00:12.610
something very important I have
to do right at this very minute.

00:12.611 --> 00:13.945
Yeah, what's that, Wood?

00:15.821 --> 00:19.617
Did you... need to take
some medication?

00:19.618 --> 00:21.520
No.

00:23.005 --> 00:26.224
Well, uh... maybe you're
supposed to call somebody, huh?

00:26.226 --> 00:28.826
No. No...

00:28.827 --> 00:30.095
Perhaps you had an appointment?

00:30.096 --> 00:32.464
Maybe if I just
don't think about it,

00:32.497 --> 00:34.966
it'll come to me.

00:34.967 --> 00:36.350
I wouldn't worry
about it, Wood.

00:36.351 --> 00:37.619
As you get older, you know,

00:37.620 --> 00:39.420
the memory starts to go a bit.

00:39.421 --> 00:41.155
Myself, I was
thinking about maybe

00:41.156 --> 00:43.326
signing up for one of
those memory classes.

00:43.409 --> 00:45.509
That's it, my memory class!

00:48.180 --> 00:49.614
Today's graduation.

00:53.119 --> 00:55.103
Oh, where'd I park?

00:55.137 --> 00:58.139
Oh, yeah.
See, it's working.

00:58.173 --> 01:01.108
(theme song begins)

01:02.911 --> 01:05.346
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:05.381 --> 01:09.818
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:11.120 --> 01:15.757
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:15.791 --> 01:18.026
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:18.060 --> 01:20.595
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:20.630 --> 01:24.900
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

